msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah! Wandering around here and listening\n"
"to anecdotes about <2.se_co>Champion Revali<3.re_co>\n"
"has truly invigorated me.\n"
"<4.se_co><5.an><6.re_co>In fact, it has inspired me to honor\n"
"him in my own way, separate from\n"
"my teacher's <7.se_co>unfinished song<8.re_co>.\n"
"<9.so>That is why I felt inclined to roost here,\n"
"near the <10.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Medoh<11.re_co>,\n"
"which <12.se_co>Revali <13.re_co>himself mastered."
